    "description": {
        "en-US": "This addon provides “Smart” quote support for Thunderbird Email.\n\nTo use this addon:\n\n<ol>\t<li>Install the addon as normal</li>\t<li>Open a new message window</li>\t<li>Right-Click on the tool bar and select <b>Customize …</b></li>\t<li>Drag the two Smart Quote buttons to the toolbar</li></ol>\n<b>Convert to Typographic Quotes</b> converts selected text with \"straight\" quotes to text using proper typographic quotes.\n<b>Smart Quotes</b> enables or disables Auto Smart Quotes. Smart quotes will be entered as you type. You can enter a Straight quote by holding the control key as you type a quote. To turn off Auto Smart Quotes, click on the button again.\n\nMore information on Smart Quotes may be found at <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://outgoing.prod.mozaws.net/v1/49d025bb144a34a6b8cf161ed984a62bac8d6d284754feedde419f089f023736/http%3A//www.smartquotes.info\">http://www.smartquotes.info</a>."
    },
